      "title": "Model Info — usage",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "Connect any model type (MODEL, CLIP, VAE…). After execution the node displays architecture details directly on the canvas.\n\nOutputs: **class_name** (Python class, e.g. `WAN21`, `Flux`), **dim** (hidden dimension), **label** (title of the upstream node).\n\nUseful for debugging pipelines, confirming which model is on a bus, or routing based on model type with a Switch node."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
